rVenue.name: CITADEL SECURITIES LLC
rVenue.materialAspects: Citadel Execution Services: Firstrade Securities Inc. receives payment from the third party venue Citadel Securities, LLC for directing order flow of listed equities to this venue. The disclosed amounts represent the total amount of payments received by Firstrade Securities Inc. Renumeration is paid on a per share basis. For additional detailed Routing Information, please refer to: Citadel Securities, LLC, https://www.citadelsecurities.com/rule-605-606-statements/
